commit.message: Increment version number for next development cycle
Align with other branches. No functional change.
News links should be in reverse date order
Add a version to the title
Update OpenSSL 3.0.x patch for addition of INT64_MAx constant
Fix typo. Further improve BZ 67818 wording
BZ 67818: SSL#setVerify()/SSLContext#setVerify() silently set undocumented default verify paths

Remove an unreachable if condition around CRLs in sslcontext.c

SSL_CTX_get_cert_store() will never return NULL because it is initialized at
context creation time with X509_STORE_new() and unless we have set it explicitly
to NULL with SSL_CTX_set_cert_store().
BZ 67538: Make use of Ant's <javaversion /> task to enfore the mininum Java build version
Add Ant version (1.10.2) requirement identical to Tomcat
Align Java source compile configuration with Tomcat
BZ 67616: o.a.tomcat.jni.SSL contains useless check for old OpenSSL version
Align default pass phrase prompt with HTTPd on Windows as well
BZ 67615: Windows binary for version 2 has incorrect version suffix compared to the GNU autoconf version
